messages.messageBody:
I ABSOLUTELY love the Boise-Co-op!!!!! My little ones are
still a little small to bring to Boondocks, but it looks
fun. That is neat that you live in Ketchum. You will have to
let me know if you come this way again. Maybe we could meet.
It is nice to meet others with the same values and ideas you
have.
kim myers
